d you choose?","DataExportTag":"hedcare_prodchoice","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"After seeing the AI recommendation, which option would you choose?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Product A"},"2":{"Display":"Product B"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID10","Randomization":{"Advanced":null,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"All"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_esQlyr1TzlT24qW","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID11","SecondaryAttribute":"You are invited to participate in a short study about consumer decision-making.\u00a0This study will t..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"You are invited to participate in a short study about consumer decision-making.&nbsp;This study will take approximately 8\u201310 minutes to complete.&nbsp;<br><br>Your responses are anonymous and will be used for research purposes only.&nbsp;You may withdraw at any time.&nbsp;<br><br>This study contains two attention checks. Upon passing these checks, you will earn tokens that you can spend within the experiment.&nbsp;<br><br>By clicking <b>\"I Agree,\"<\/b> you consent to participate.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Consent","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"You are invited to participate in a short study about consumer decision-making.\u00a0This study will t...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I Agree - I consent to participate"},"2":{"Display":"I Do Not Agree - I do not wish to participate"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID11"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_esQlyr1TzlT24qW","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID12","SecondaryAttribute":"In this study, you will be asked to make a product choice on a new AI-powered website, SmartKart....","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this study, you will be asked to make a product choice on a new AI-powered website, <i>SmartKart.com<\/i>. The platform uses a&nbsp;proprietary AI that learns from your interactions and provides personalized product recommendations.<br><br>You are browsing the site today to purchase a product. You will see several options and receive a recommendation from an AI assistant designed to help inform your decision. After reviewing the options, you will select the product you prefer. <br><br>Upon successfully answering the questions in the next section, you will earn tokens that you can spend upon each product. This helps us understand your willingness to pay for the product. Please note that tokens can only be used within the experiment and cannot be exchanged for real currency.&nbsp;<br><br>At the end of the study, participants will be randomly selected to receive the product they chose, delivered via Amazon. Please make your selection carefully, as you may receive the product you select.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Instructions","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this study, you will be asked to make a product choice on a new AI-powered website, SmartKart....","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID12"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_esQlyr1TzlT24qW","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID13","SecondaryAttribute":"In this task, what will you do?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this task, what will you do?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Attention Check - 1","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this task, what will you do?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Choose a product"},"2":{"Display":"Write a paragraph"},"3":{"Display":"Solve math problems"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[{"ChoiceID":"1","Grades":{"SC_6sw6HWzoH3XdMlo":"1"},"index":0}],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID13","Randomization":{"Advanced":null,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"All"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_esQlyr1TzlT24qW","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID14","SecondaryAttribute":"You have now earned 10 tokens for the next task.\u00a0 \u00a0You are choosing ice cream for yourself. Here..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:660px;margin:0 auto 16px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong>You have now earned <u>10<\/u> tokens for the next task.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong>&nbsp;You are choosing ice cream for yourself. <\/strong>Here are the two products.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83c\udf66<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Product A<\/span><br><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">A smooth and creamy vanilla ice cream made with real vanilla bean for a rich, classic flavor.<\/span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/strong><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\"><b>\ud83c\udf66<\/b><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;\">Product B<\/span><br><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">A smooth and creamy vanilla ice cream with a balanced, classic vanilla flavor and a soft texture.<\/span><\/strong><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\"><strong>You have <u>5 tokens<\/u> for each ice cream.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\">For each ice cream option, please indicate <strong>the maximum number of tokens(0-5 tokens) you would be willing to spend<\/strong>. Please answer for both products.&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"You have now earned 10 tokens for the next task.\u00a0 \u00a0You are choosing ice cream for yourself. Here...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Product A"},"2":{"Display":"Product B"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":7,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"0"},"2":{"Display":"1"},"3":{"Display":"2"},"4":{"Display":"3"},"5":{"Display":"4"},"6":{"Display":"5"}},"AnswerOrder":[1,2,3,4,5,"6"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:660px;margin:0 auto 16px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong>Imagine you are choosing a dessert for yourself.<br>\nYou want to select an option that you would personally enjoy.<\/strong><br>\nBelow, you will see two ice cream options.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83c\udf66<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#222;margin-bottom:4px;\">Product A<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.5;\">Rich and smooth, with a full-bodied flavor.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83c\udf66<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#222;margin-bottom:4px;\">Product B<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.5;\">Soft and airy, with a subtle and refreshing flavor.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\">For each product, please indicate the maximum number of tokens you would be willing to pay, from <strong>1<\/strong> (very low willingness to pay) to <strong>5<\/strong> (very high willingness to pay).<\/div>\n<\/div>","DataExportTag":"hedeff_pre_wtp","QuestionID":"QID14","Randomization":{"Advanced":null,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"All"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_esQlyr1TzlT24qW","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID15","SecondaryAttribute":"\ud83c\udf66 Product A A smooth and creamy vanilla ice cream made with real vanilla bean for a rich, classic","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:660px;margin:0 auto 16px;\">\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83c\udf66<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Product A<\/span><br><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">A smooth and creamy vanilla ice cream made with real vanilla bean for a rich, classic flavor.<\/span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/strong><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83c\udf66<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;\">Product B<\/span><br><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">A smooth and creamy vanilla ice cream with a balanced, classic vanilla flavor and a soft texture.<\/span><\/strong><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;background:#f5f5f5;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n<div style=\"width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;background:#888;color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\">AI<\/div>\n\n<div>\n<div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#555;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-bottom:5px;\">AI Recommendation<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#444;line-height:1.7;\"><b>Product B.<\/b> This option ranks higher on key attributes. It delivers a smooth texture, consistent flavor, and reliable overall quality. Based on these factors, it is the stronger selection.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\"><strong>After seeing the AI recommendation<\/strong>, please indicate the maximum number of tokens you would be willing to pay (0-5 tokens) for each product.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"\ud83c\udf66 Product A A smooth and creamy vanilla ice cream made with real vanilla bean for a rich, classic...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Product A"},"2":{"Display":"Product B"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":7,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"0"},"2":{"Display":"1"},"3":{"Display":"2"},"4":{"Display":"3"},"5":{"Display":"4"},"6":{"Display":"5"}},"AnswerOrder":[1,2,3,4,5,"6"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:660px;margin:0 auto 16px;\">\n  <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n      <div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justi