re choosing dish detergent for your home....","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Product A"},"2":{"Display":"Product B"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":7,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"0"},"2":{"Display":"1"},"3":{"Display":"2"},"4":{"Display":"3"},"5":{"Display":"4"},"6":{"Display":"5"}},"AnswerOrder":[1,2,3,4,5,"6"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:660px;margin:0 auto 16px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong>You are choosing dish detergent for your house.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong>You want to select an option that you would personally prefer.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;\">Below you will see two options, please select one.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83e\uddf4<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#222;margin-bottom:4px;\">Product A<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.5;\">Strong grease-cutting power, able to wipe the toughest stains away<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83e\uddf4<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#222;margin-bottom:4px;\">Product B<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666;line-height:1.5;\">Gentle formula with no residue, softer on your hands<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\">For each product, please indicate the maximum number of tokens you would be willing to pay, from <strong>1<\/strong> (very low willingness to pay) to <strong>5<\/strong> (very high willingness to pay).<\/div>\n<\/div>","DataExportTag":"utileff_pre_wtp","QuestionID":"QID23","Randomization":{"Advanced":null,"TotalRandSubset":"","Type":"All"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_esQlyr1TzlT24qW","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID24","SecondaryAttribute":"\ud83e\uddf4 Product A A liquid dish detergent designed to effectively remove grease while being suitable fo","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"font-family:sans-serif;max-width:660px;margin:0 auto 16px;\">\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83e\uddf4<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Product A<\/span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;\">A liquid dish detergent designed to effectively remove grease while being suitable for everyday dishwashing.<\/span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> <\/span><\/strong><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #ddd;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\">\n<div style=\"height:100px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:44px;background:#fafafa;\">\ud83e\uddf4<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"padding:12px 14px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); margin-bottom: 4px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Product B<\/span><br><span style=\"font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;\">A liquid dish detergent designed to cut through grease efficiently while remaining suitable for everyday use.<\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;background:#f5f5f5;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n<div style=\"width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;background:#888;color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;\">AI<\/div>\n\n<div>\n<div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#555;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;margin-bottom:5px;\">AI Recommendation<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#444;line-height:1.7;\"><b>Product B.<\/b> This option performs better on core cleaning metrics. It removes grease efficiently while maintaining consistency across repeated use. Based on these attributes, it is the more effective choice.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\"><strong>After seeing the AI recommendation<\/strong>, please indicate the maximum number of tokens you would be willing to pay (0-5 tokens) for each product.<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\"><\/div>\n<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"\ud83e\uddf4 Product A A liquid dish detergent designed to effectively remove grease while being suitable fo...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Product A"},"2":{"Display":"Product B"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"